00Z","msg":"全民岳巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岳義精神 打狗救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff21f082f67bf6096ba1a96d257a9ba518cdbf1","tid":1573114,"uid":128994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:52:03.000Z","msg":"推口號<br />\n一直以黎梁天琦既口號都深入民心， 呢個係其中一個咁多人支持我哋嘅原因<br />\n嗌口號係不斷洗腦嘅方法，咁大家嗌得多嘅時候，手足們聽得多，就會感覺到大家都有呢個共識，就會自動自覺去救人。"},{"pid":"18458fef2107df4ed70cfe39f8df77ebbdce8780","tid":1573114,"uid":274161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:08:23.000Z","msg":"大把忠義英雄唔講，係要講雷鋒呢個中共用以洗腦塑造出來的典型"},{"pid":"22a91447963c7ed88f2e718ad2aaa0bfe5604ec3","tid":1573114,"uid":37413,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"bcc4d833b5a23c5afb4aa7c4abcc3fce88731eb1","tid":1573114,"uid":55309,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:32:42.000Z","msg":"個頭爆哂成地血一句聲都無叫過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:30:59.000Z","msg":"最令人敬重就係呢樣嘢，有好多手足比人捉咗打會喊晒口大叫好痛唔好打之類<br />\n佢真係冇哼過一聲，令死不屈精神令人敬重<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68403959cb86d80824747004b1bfc69f28946c1d","tid":1573114,"uid":54785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"18458fef2107df4ed70cfe39f8df77ebbdce8780","tid":1573114,"uid":274161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:08:23.000Z","msg":"大把忠義英雄唔講，係要講雷鋒呢個中共用以洗腦塑造出來的典型"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T03:35:30.000Z","msg":"連登用毛語錄用得好成功喎，我地要全民效法岳義，就要好似當年中共咁對利他行為作鋪天蓋地式嘅宣傳<br />\n<br />\n英雄造時勢，時勢造英雄。香港得一個岳義係無用的。<br />\n<br />\n全民都要：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">